<heading>session list - Show active sessions.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  session list
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Lists all active runtime sessions.  The current session
is marked with an asterisk.
</paragraph>

<paragraph>
Each row shows the session key, number of connected clients,
homes, and running flows.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
current, attach, detach, man
</paragraph>
